[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說大乘入諸佛境界智光明莊",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261a08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "嚴經卷第四",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261a09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譯經三藏朝散大夫試光祿卿傳梵",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261a11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大師賜紫沙門臣惟淨等奉　詔譯",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261a12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「妙吉祥！",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261a13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩提者與虛空等，謂以虛空無高、無下，菩提亦然無高、無下，由是如來成等正覺。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261a13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "雖成正覺，亦無少法如微塵許若高若下諸所施作，此如是法若如是，知即是實智。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261a15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "妙吉祥！",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261a17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以何義故名為實智？",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261a17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂一切法了無根本、無生無滅，彼無實性亦無所得，若有實性即是滅法，彼雖有生而無主宰復無攝受。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261a17_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "妙吉祥！",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261a20_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若無主宰、無攝受法即是滅法，此等諸法若生若滅，當知皆是緣法所轉，亦非此中有少法可轉，然佛如來不於諸法說斷滅相。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261a20_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，妙吉祥！",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261a24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩提者即是如說句。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261a24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以何義故名如說句？",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261a24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如說句者即是菩提。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261a25_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如其菩提，色、受、想、行、識亦然，而不離真如；如其菩提，眼、耳、鼻、舌、身、意，色、聲、香、味、觸、法處亦然，而不離真如；如其菩提，眼界、色界、眼識界，耳界、聲界、耳識界，鼻界、香界、鼻識界，舌界、味界、舌識界，身界、觸界、身識界，意界、法界、意識界亦然，而不離真如；如其菩提，地界、水界、火界、風界亦然，而不離真如。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261a25_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此等諸法如是施設，其所施設謂蘊、處、界，由是如來成等正覺，所成正覺離顛倒法。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261b03_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如其先法，後法亦然、中法亦然，前際不生、後際不去、中際性離，此如是法是即名為如所說句。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261b05_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如其一法，多法亦然；如其多法，一法亦然。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261b07_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "妙吉祥！",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261b08_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若一性若多性皆無所得，若有相、若無相，無入無住。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261b08_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何名為相？",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261b09_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何名無相？",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261b09_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所言相者，謂即生起一切善法；言無相者，謂一切法無所得故。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261b10_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又相者，謂即心無所住分位；無相者，即無相三摩地解脫法門。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261b11_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又相者，即一切法思惟稱量算數伺察；無相者，謂出過稱量。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261b12_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何名出過稱量？",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261b14_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂識法無故。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261b14_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又相者，即有為伺察；無相者，即無為伺察。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261b14_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，妙吉祥！",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261b16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩提者即是無漏無取。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261b16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何名無漏？",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261b16_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何名無取？",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261b17_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無漏者，謂離四種有漏之法。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261b17_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為四？",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261b17_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者欲漏，二者有漏，三者無明漏，四者見漏。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261b18_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無取者，謂離四種取著之法。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261b19_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為四？",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261b19_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者欲取，二者見取，三者戒禁取，四者我語取。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261b20_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是四取，悉由無明暗蔽、愛法滋潤，互相取著。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261b21_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "妙吉祥！",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261b22_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若或本初於我語取根本，能了知者即我清淨，我清淨已隨知一切眾生清淨，由我清淨故即彼一切眾生清淨，若一切眾生清淨即法無二、無二種類，彼無二義即無生、無滅。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261b22_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "妙吉祥！",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261b26_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若無生、無滅即無心意識可轉，若無心意識可轉即無分別，若無分別即深固作意相應無明不能發起，若彼無明不發起者即十二有支亦不生長，若十二有支不生長者即法無生，若法無生即法決定，若法決定即調伏義，若調伏義即是勝義，若其勝義即離補特伽羅義，若離補特伽羅義即不可說義，若不可說義即緣生義，若緣生義即是法義，若法義即如來義。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261b26_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是所說，若見緣生即能見法，若能見法即見如來，彼諸所見，若其如理審伺察時，是中亦無少法可見。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261c05_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "妙吉祥！",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261c08_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何名少法？",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261c08_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂心所緣。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261c08_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若無心所緣即無所見，由如是法故如來成等正覺，平等故平等。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261c08_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，妙吉祥！",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261c11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩提者，是清淨義、無垢義、無著義。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261c11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何名清淨？",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261c12_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何名無垢？",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261c12_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何名無著？",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261c12_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂空解脫門即是清淨；無相解脫門即是無垢；無願解脫門即是無著。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261c12_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無生是清淨；無作意是無垢；無起是無著。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261c14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自性是清淨；圓淨是無垢。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261c15_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "明亮是無著。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261c15_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無戲論是清淨；離戲論是無垢；戲論寂止是無著。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261c16_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "真如是清淨；法界是無垢；實際是無著。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261c17_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "虛空是清淨；寥廓是無垢；廣大是無著。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261c18_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "了知內法是清淨；外無所行是無垢；內外無所得是無著。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261c19_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "了知蘊法是清淨；界法自性是無垢；離諸處法是無著。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261c20_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "過去盡智是清淨；未來無生智是無垢；現在法界安住智是無著。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261c21_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "妙吉祥！",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261c23_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此如是等，清淨、無垢、無著諸義，於一句中普能攝入，謂寂靜句。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261c23_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若寂靜即遍寂，若遍寂即近寂，若近寂即寂止，若寂止此說即是大牟尼法。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261c24_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，妙吉祥！",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261c27_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如其虛空，菩提亦然；如其菩提，諸法亦然；如其諸法，眾生亦然；如其眾生，剎土亦然；如其剎土，涅盤亦然。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261c27_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "妙吉祥！",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261c29_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此說即是涅盤平等，為一切法畢竟邊際清淨之因，無對治離對治因，本來清淨、本來無垢、本來無著。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0261c29_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來了知彼一切法如是相故，現成正覺，然後觀察諸眾生界，建立清淨、無垢、無著遊戲法門，以是名字於諸眾生大悲心轉。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262a03_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，妙吉祥！",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262a06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何是菩薩所行？",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262a06_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩勝行？",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262a06_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂若菩薩無盡無不盡、無生無不生，於畢竟盡相無所領受，然亦不壞畢竟無生。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262a06_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "妙吉祥！",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262a08_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若如是行，是為菩薩勝行。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262a08_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，妙吉祥！",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262a10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩於過去心已盡，此無所行；未來心未至，此無所行；現在心無住，此無所行。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262a10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩於其過去、未來、現在諸心悉無所著，菩薩若如是行，是為菩薩勝行。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262a12_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又復布施之法，諸佛如來與諸菩薩，而無其二無二種類，菩薩若如是行，是為菩薩勝行。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262a14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "持戒、忍辱、精進、禪定、智慧亦復如是，諸佛如來與諸菩薩，而無其二無二種類，菩薩若如是行，是為菩薩勝行。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262a16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，妙吉祥！",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262a19_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩不行色空、不行色不空，菩薩若如是行，是為菩薩勝行。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262a19_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262a20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "色即是空、色自性空，受想行識亦復如是，是故不行識空、不行識不空，菩薩若如是行，是為菩薩勝行。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262a20_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262a23_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂心意識無所得故。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262a23_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "妙吉祥！",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262a23_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此中無少法可有，若知若斷、若修若證，悉無所有。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262a24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由如是故，此說名盡。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262a25_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是乃為畢竟盡相，若畢竟盡即無所盡，無盡亦無盡。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262a25_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262a26_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如所說盡故。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262a27_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若如所說盡，彼即無法可盡，若無法可盡即是無為，若無為即無生亦無滅，若佛出世、若不出世法性常住，以法住故即是法界，如法界住故智無所轉亦非無轉，以智無轉非無轉故，如是法理若悟入者，即得無漏、無生、無滅，此名漏盡。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262a27_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "妙吉祥！",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262b03_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故當知，雖復世俗音聲文字總聚施設，是中無有少法若生、若滅。」",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262b03_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，妙吉祥童真菩薩摩訶薩即從座起，偏袒右肩右膝著地向佛合掌，以妙伽陀伸讚歎曰：「無形顯色無狀貌，　　是中無滅亦無生，　無住亦復根本無，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262b06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　以無住故無出入，　　亦復無彼諸分位，　已能解脫六處門，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262b11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　一切法中無所住，　　有性無性皆遠離，　諸行平等得圓成，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262b13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　已能出離於三界，　　虛空平等性中住，　世間諸欲不染心，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262b15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　三摩呬多常安處，　　行住坐臥亦復然，　諸威儀事妙肅成，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262b17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　平等而來平等去，　　平等性中妙安住，　不壞平等性法門，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262b19_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　大聖善入平等性，　　諸法皆住等引心，　遍入無相妙法門，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262b21_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　大聖無住無所緣，　　定中高積慧峯峻，　普遍諸法得圓成，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262b23_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　眾生威儀及色相，　　語言音聲亦復然，　普能示現剎那間，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262b25_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　大聖已離於名色，　　於蘊界法亦普斷，　復能善入無相門，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262b27_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　大聖善離於諸相，　　諸相境界亦遠離，　已能善入無相門，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262b29_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　無所思惟無分別，　　淨意亦復無所住，　無諸作意無念生，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262c02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　譬如虛空無含藏，　　已離戲論無所著，　其心平等復如空，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262c04_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　譬如虛空無中邊，　　諸佛法性亦如是，　已能超越三世門，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262c06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　諸佛猶如虛空相，　　即此虛空亦無相，　已能解脫事及因，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262c08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　一切法中無依止，　　如水中月無所取，　無我相亦無音聲，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262c10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　大聖不依止蘊法，　　界處諸法亦復然，　已能解脫顛倒心，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262c12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　大聖已離於二邊，　　亦復斷除於我見，　法界平等得圓成，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262c14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　色相名數已解脫，　　亦復遠離不正法，　無取無捨平等心，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262c16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　已能超越諸魔法，　　一切法中悉通達，　妙入無障礙法門，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262c18_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　正智不說諸法有，　　亦復不說諸法無，　無語言道無發生，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262c20_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　聖不依止於二法，　　久已摧折我慢幢，　解脫二無二法門，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262c22_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　所有身語意過失，　　大聖久已普除斷，　不可譬喻不可思，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262c24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　大聖無轉無發悟，　　一切過失悉遠離，　智為先導遍所行，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262c26_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　無漏淨念最微妙，　　實不實法悉了知，　亦無繫著無思惟，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0262c28_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　大聖於心無所緣，　　而能遍知一切心，　亦無自他想念生，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0263a01_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　無所緣中有所緣，　　於一切心不迷著，　無障礙法已圓明，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0263a03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　大聖於心無所緣，　　亦復自性無所有，　無心平等得圓成，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0263a05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　大聖不依於智法，　　而能遍觀諸剎土，　一切眾生行亦然，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0263a07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　智者於心無所得，　　是中亦復畢竟無，　於一切法正遍知，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0263a09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　知一切法皆如幻，　　即此幻亦無所有，　已能解脫幻法門，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0263a11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　正覺雖行於世間，　　亦不依止於世法，　復無世間分別心，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0263a13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　大聖於彼空中行，　　由空所成空境界，　空與非空聖所宣，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0263a15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　現大神通起化事，　　悉依如幻三摩地，　離種種性遍入門，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0263a17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　了知非一非多性，　　若近若遠無所轉，　無高無下平等心，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0263a19_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　金剛喻定現在前，　　一剎那中成正覺，　遍入無對礙法門，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0263a21_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　雖知涅盤無所動，　　亦於三世善調伏，　具足種種方便門，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0263a23_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　於彼一切眾生類，　　善解智慧及方便，　然亦不動涅盤門，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0263a25_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　大聖無相無發悟，　　已離戲論無對礙，　無我故無對礙心，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0263a27_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　已離疑惑無過失，　　無我我所亦復然，　於一切處正遍知，　　無所緣尊今讚禮。",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0263a29_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說大乘入諸佛境界智光明莊嚴經卷第四",
        "from": "T12n0359_004:0263b02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]